enlit=E2=80=94the result, of course, of the changing economics of the movie=
 business, in general, and comedy films, in particular. It=E2=80=99s a meta=
phor for how industries change, and The Judd Apatow Sign of the Times ( htt=
ps://puck.news/judd-apatow-is-not-laughing/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Backstory+-+=
